OL,3,CDrones and AI in #800m Budget package
OL,4,Cto cut police and NHS times
OL,6,FThe will include an #800 million
OL,7,Fpackage of technology reforms that is
OL,8,Fdesigned to speed-up results in the
OL,9,FNHS and cut admin tasks for police.
OL,11,FChancellor Jeremy Hunt said there is
OL,12,F"too much waste in the system" as he
OL,13,Fannounced on Sunday a series of
OL,14,Fmeasures to free-up time for those on
OL,15,Fthe front line of public services.
