OL,3,CDrones and AI in #800m Budget package
OL,4,Cto cut police and NHS times
OL,6,FAs part of the Treasury reforms,
OL,7,Fpolice will use drones to assess
OL,8,Fincidents such as traffic collisions
OL,9,Fand artificial intelligence (AI) will
OL,10,Fbe deployed to cut scan times by a
OL,11,Fthird.
OL,13,FThe department said the changes, due
OL,14,Fto be in Wednesday's Budget, have the
OL,15,Fpotential to deliver #1.8 billion
OL,16,Fworth of benefits to public sector
OL,17,Fproductivity by 2029.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/12
