OL,3,CDrones and AI in #800m Budget package
OL,4,Cto cut police and NHS times
OL,6,FIn the health sector, the Treasury
OL,7,Fsaid that more than 130,000 patients a
OL,8,Fyear, including those waiting for
OL,9,Fcancer results, can expect to receive
OL,10,Ftheir test results sooner as a result
OL,11,Fof at least 100 MRI scanners in
OL,12,FEngland being upgraded with AI.
OL,14,FThe pioneering technology will be
OL,15,Ftrained to recognise patterns in scans
OL,16,Fthrough machine-learning which
OL,17,Fofficials said could cut scan times by
OL,18,Fover a third.
