OL,3,CDrones and AI in #800m Budget package
OL,4,Cto cut police and NHS times
OL,6,FIn policing, the Treasury said its
OL,7,Freforms will help to deliver on the
OL,8,FPolice Productivity Review, which it
OL,9,Fsaid found that up to 38 million hours
OL,10,Fof officer time could be saved every
OL,11,Fyear.
OL,13,FMr Hunt will provide #230 million
OL,14,Ftowards the rollout of time-saving
OL,15,Ftechnology, including funding
OL,16,Fautomated redaction of personal
OL,17,Finformation during evidence collation.
