OL,4,Cto cut police and NHS times
OL,6,FThe process will apply to name badges
OL,7,Fin shoplifting incidents, irrelevant
OL,8,Ffaces from body worn cameras and
OL,9,Fnumber plates from video evidence.
OL,11,FInterviewing witnesses and victims via
OL,12,Fvideo call will be approved to improve
OL,13,Fspeed of service.
OL,15,FA pilot allowing officers to use
OL,16,Fdrones to first respond to some
OL,17,Fincidents like traffic collisions will
OL,18,Falso be given the green light.
