OL,6,FThe drone information will be fed back
OL,7,Fto help forces to assess the
OL,8,Fseriousness of the incident and the
OL,9,Fresources required to deal with it,
OL,10,Fthe Treasury said.
OL,12,FAI will be used on the 101 non-
OL,13,Femergency service to triage callers,
OL,14,Fit added.
