OL,3,CDrones and AI in #800m Budget package
OL,4,Cto cut police and NHS times
OL,6,FOfficials said the move is about
OL,7,Freversing the high spending, high tax
OL,8,Fapproach the UK government adopted to
OL,9,Fsee the country through the
OL,10,Fcoronavirus pandemic and the energy
OL,11,Fshocks sparked by Russia's invasion of
OL,12,FUkraine.
OL,14,FMr Hunt said: "We shouldn't fall into
OL,15,Fthe trap of thinking more spending
OL,16,Fbuys us better public services.
