OL,3,CDrones and AI in #800m Budget package
OL,4,Cto cut police and NHS times
OL,6,F"There is too much waste in the system
OL,7,Fand we want public servants to get
OL,8,Fback to doing what matters most:
OL,9,Fteaching our children, keeping us safe
OL,10,Fand treating us when we're sick.
OL,12,F"That's why our plan is about reaping
OL,13,Fthe rewards of productivity, from
OL,14,Ffaster access to MRIs for patients to
OL,15,Fhundreds of thousands of police hours
OL,16,Ffreed up to attend burglaries or
OL,17,Fincidents of domestic abuse."
