OL,6,FDarren Jones, Labour's shadow chief
OL,7,Fsecretary to the Treasury, said the
OL,8,Fannouncement mounted to "spin without
OL,9,Fsubstance".
OL,11,F"Nothing in Britain is better off
OL,12,Fafter 14 years of Conservative
OL,13,Feconomic failure," he said.
OL,15,F"Millions of people are stuck on
OL,16,Fhospital waiting lists, our schools
OL,17,Fare crumbling and our streets are less
OL,18,Fsafe. And yet all the Chancellor is
OL,19,Foffering is more spin without
OL,20,Fsubstance.
