OL,4,Cto cut police and NHS times
OL,6,F"It's time for change. Only Labour
OL,7,Foffers a long-term plan to grow our
OL,8,Feconomy to deliver more jobs, more
OL,9,Finvestment and to put more money in
OL,10,Fpeople's pockets."
OL,12,FMr Hunt is under pressure to deliver
OL,13,Ftax cuts in what could be the last
OL,14,Ffiscal statement from the Conservative
OL,15,Fgovernment before the next general
OL,16,Felection, which is widely expected in
OL,17,Fthe autumn.
