OL,6,FWith the Chancellor number-crunching
OL,7,Fover the coming days before finalising
OL,8,Fhis Budget, official forecasts of the
OL,9,FChancellor's "head room" against his
OL,10,Fplans to get borrowing to fall in five
OL,11,Fyears' time are understood to have
OL,12,Fmoved against the government.
OL,14,FTreasury sources this week said Mr
OL,15,FHunt is considering a further squeeze
OL,16,Fon public spending as a way to deliver
OL,17,Fthe tax cuts being demanded by some
OL,18,FTory MPs.
